[[File:Bucket detail.png|left|100px|A detailed image of a bucket.]]
A '''bucket''' is one of the most common items available in ''[[RuneScape]]''. They can be purchased cheaply from most [[general store]]s and can also be found in many locations throughout the game. Buckets are commonly used for [[skills]] such as [[Crafting]], [[Cooking]] and [[Farming]]. 

{{Clear|left}}

Buckets can contain any of the following items:

*[[Water]]
*[[Bucket of sand|Sand]]
*[[Milk]] or [[Chocolatey milk]]
*[[Compost]], [[Supercompost]], or [[Ultracompost]]
*[[Slime]]
*[[Apple mush]]
*[[Bucket of sandworms|Sandworms]]
*Various quest items such as [[Bucket of wax|wax]], [[Bucket of sap|sap]], a [[hangover cure]], [[Ugthanki dung|camel dung]], and [[weird gloop]]

One convenient way to obtain up to an inventory of buckets quickly is to have a [[house]] that has a larder; from which you can remove buckets of milk, to be emptied. This is also the fastest way to get milk.

A convenient way to obtain buckets in bulk is to purchase [[Empty bucket pack]]s containing 100 noted empty buckets. These packs can be bought at [[general store]]s and [[farming shop]]s for 500–875 [[coins]] each depending on the stock available.

Note that one may deposit and withdraw up to 1000 buckets from the [[Tool leprechaun]]s located at almost every [[Farming/Patch locations|Farming patch]]; no [[Farming]] level is required to do this.

